{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/javascript-como-fazer-smoothScroll/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"JS para impacientes"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"f95e3b95-70b2-52f0-b570-e5de739790d8","excerpt":"Smoothly scrolls the element on which it’s called into the visible area of the browser window. Use  method to scroll the element. \nPass  to  so it scrolls…","html":"<p>Smoothly scrolls the element on which it’s called into the visible area of the browser window.</p>\n<p>Use <code class=\"language-text\">.scrollIntoView</code> method to scroll the element.\nPass <code class=\"language-text\">{ behavior: &#39;smooth&#39; }</code> to <code class=\"language-text\">.scrollIntoView</code> so it scrolls smoothly.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-js line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">smoothScroll</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">element</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span>\n  document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>element<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">scrollIntoView</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    behavior<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'smooth'</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-js line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token function\">smoothScroll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'#fooBar'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// scrolls smoothly to the element with the id fooBar</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">smoothScroll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'.fooBar'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// scrolls smoothly to the first element with a class of fooBar</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p><a href=\"http://github.com/30-seconds/\">Acesse a Referência original</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"como usar o smoothScroll no javascript es6","date":"January 04, 2020","description":""}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/javascript-como-fazer-smoothScroll/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/javascript-como-fazer-sortCharactersInString/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"como usar o sortCharactersInString no javascript es6"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/javascript-como-fazer-sleep/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"como usar o sleep no javascript es6"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["1061827086","63159454"]}